  "id": "RAW_65ee9c8d",
  "title": "1 分钟跑出数百预测！WeatherNext 2 把短时预报带入小时级",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI3MTA0MTk1MA==&mid=2652647690&idx=3&sn=9d57a1d2acfa0abae16008aad104dbc8",
  "date": "2025-11-21 09:08:00",
